是如何由
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\boldsymbol{a}}$
\end_inset

恒等为零的要求确定的，这是参考姿态是最优姿态估计的条件。利用方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:13"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)计算时间导数，使用方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:8"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)和(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:23"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，给出
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left[\begin{array}{c}
\boldsymbol{\omega}\\
0
\end{array}\right]\otimes q=2\dfrac{\mathrm{d}[\delta q(\boldsymbol{a})]}{\mathrm{d}t}\otimes q_{\mathrm{ref}}+\delta q(\boldsymbol{a})\otimes\left[\begin{array}{c}
\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{ref}}\\
0
\end{array}\right]\otimes q_{\mathrm{ref}}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
用方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:13"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)代替左侧的
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

，用整个方程式乘以
\begin_inset Formula $q_{\mathrm{ref}}$
\end_inset

的倒数，然后重新排列得到
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
2\dfrac{\mathrm{d}[\delta q(\boldsymbol{a})]}{\mathrm{d}t}=\left[\begin{array}{c}
\boldsymbol{\omega}\\
0
\end{array}\right]\otimes\delta q(\boldsymbol{a})-\delta q(\boldsymbol{a})\otimes\left[\begin{array}{c}
\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{ref}}\\
0
\end{array}\right]\label{eq:25}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
常用的EKF技术，将
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\omega}$
\end_inset

的非线性函数的期望值近似为其期望值
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\boldsymbol{a}}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\boldsymbol{\omega}}$
\end_inset

的同一个非线性函数，给出
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
2\dfrac{\mathrm{d}[\delta q(\hat{\boldsymbol{a}})]}{\mathrm{d}t}=\left[\begin{array}{c}
\hat{\boldsymbol{\omega}}\\
0
\end{array}\right]\otimes\delta q(\hat{\boldsymbol{a}})-\delta q(\hat{\boldsymbol{a}})\otimes\left[\begin{array}{c}
\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{ref}}\\
0
\end{array}\right]\label{eq:26}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
请注意，
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{ref}}$
\end_inset

不是随机变量。
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\boldsymbol{a}}$
\end_inset

为零的要求意味着
\begin_inset Formula $\delta q(\hat{\boldsymbol{a}})$
\end_inset

是特征四元数，所以恒量，因此方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:26"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)给出
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{ref}}(t)=\hat{\boldsymbol{\omega}}(t)\label{eq:27}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:23"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)和(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:27"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)指定的四元数传播，与用常规方法推导的传播方程相同。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
现在我们专门研究一组陀螺仪用来获得角速度信息来代替航天器动力学模型的情况[8,9]。我们采用了Farrenkopf的陀螺动力学误差模型[30]，这意味着我们忽略
了速率积分陀螺的输出噪声[31]。这是导航级陀螺仪的最佳近似值。角速度向量根据陀螺仪输出向量
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{out}}(t)$
\end_inset

给出，由
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{\omega}(t)=\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{out}}(t)-\boldsymbol{b}(t)-\boldsymbol{\eta}_{1}(t)\label{eq:28}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中陀螺漂移向量
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{b}(t)$
\end_inset

服从
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\dot{\boldsymbol{b}}(t)=\boldsymbol{\eta}_{2}(t)\label{eq:29}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\eta}_{1}(t)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\eta}_{2}(t)$
\end_inset

是零均值白噪声过程。估计角速度为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{\boldsymbol{\omega}}(t)=\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{out}}(t)-\hat{\boldsymbol{b}}(t)\label{eq:30}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
卡尔曼滤波器估计
\begin_inset Formula $6$
\end_inset

分量状态向量
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{x}(t)\equiv\left[\begin{array}{c}
\boldsymbol{a}(t)\\
\boldsymbol{b}(t)
\end{array}\right]
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
注意，参考四元数
\begin_inset Formula $q_{\mathrm{ref}}$
\end_inset

不是状态向量的一部分。这种状态向量的期望
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\boldsymbol{x}}(t)$
\end_inset

的传播是平凡的，因为假设
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\boldsymbol{a}}(t)$
\end_inset

恒等于零，方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:29"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)清楚地表明
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{\hat{\boldsymbol{b}}}(t)=\boldsymbol{0}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
协方差传播
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
协方差矩阵的传播
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
P(t)\equiv E\left\{ (\boldsymbol{x}-\hat{\boldsymbol{x}})(\boldsymbol{x}-\hat{\boldsymbol{x}})^{T}|Z\right\} =\left[\begin{array}{cc}
P_{a} & P_{c}\\
P_{c}^{T} & P_{b}
\end{array}\right]\label{eq:32}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

由下式给出
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\dot{P}=FP+PF^{T}+GQG^{T}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $F$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

将被确定。将协方差矩阵分为
\begin_inset Formula $3\times3$
\end_inset

的姿态、偏差和互相关(协方差)子矩阵将在以后有用。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我们考虑吉布斯向量[22]参数化的特殊性。方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:25"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)代入
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{a}_{g}=2(\delta q)_{V}/(\delta q)_{4}\label{eq:34}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中下标
\begin_inset Formula $V$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $4$
\end_inset

表示四元数的向量和标量部分，在一些简单的四元数代数之后，给出
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\dot{\boldsymbol{a}}_{g}=\left(\boldsymbol{I}_{3\times3}+\dfrac{1}{4}\boldsymbol{a}_{g}\boldsymbol{a}_{g}^{T}\right)(\boldsymbol{\omega}-\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{ref}})-\dfrac{1}{2}(\boldsymbol{\omega}+\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{ref}})\times\boldsymbol{a}_{g}\equiv\boldsymbol{f}(\boldsymbol{x},t)\label{eq:35}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这是一个精确的动力学方程，既不依赖于EKF近似，也不依赖于航天器姿态动力学模型。代入方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:27"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)、(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:28"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)和(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:30"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{\omega}-\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{ref}}=\hat{\boldsymbol{b}}-\boldsymbol{b}-\boldsymbol{\eta}_{1}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

并忽略
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}$
\end_inset

中高于一阶的项和与角速度误差的乘积，给出线性EKF近似值
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{f}(\boldsymbol{x},t)=\hat{\boldsymbol{b}}-\boldsymbol{b}-\boldsymbol{\eta}_{1}-\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{ref}}\times\boldsymbol{a}\label{eq:37}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}$
\end_inset

中的下标省略了，因为附录表明，如果用方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:18c"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)或(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:18d"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)代替方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:18b"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:37"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)同样成立。实际上，它只需要满足方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:19"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)至少一阶的表示。接下来是
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
F(t)\equiv\left[\begin{array}{cc}
\dfrac{\partial\boldsymbol{f}}{\partial\boldsymbol{a}} & \dfrac{\partial\boldsymbol{f}}{\partial\boldsymbol{b}}\\
0_{3\times3} & 0_{3\times3}
\end{array}\right]=\left[\begin{array}{cc}
-[\boldsymbol{\omega}_{\mathrm{ref}}\times] & -\boldsymbol{I}_{3\times3}\\
0_{3\times3} & 0_{3\times3}
\end{array}\right]\label{eq:38}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
G(t)\equiv\left[\begin{array}{cc}
\dfrac{\partial\boldsymbol{f}}{\partial\boldsymbol{\eta}_{1}} & \dfrac{\partial\boldsymbol{f}}{\partial\boldsymbol{\eta}_{2}}\\
0_{3\times3} & \boldsymbol{I}_{3\times3}
\end{array}\right]=\left[\begin{array}{cc}
-\boldsymbol{I}_{3\times3} & 0_{3\times3}\\
0_{3\times3} & \boldsymbol{I}_{3\times3}
\end{array}\right]
\end{equation}

\end_inset

和
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
E\left\{ \left[\begin{array}{c}
\boldsymbol{\eta}_{1}(t)\\
\boldsymbol{\eta}_{2}(t)
\end{array}\right]\left[\begin{array}{c}
\boldsymbol{\eta}_{1}(t')\\
\boldsymbol{\eta}_{2}(t')
\end{array}\right]^{T}\right\} =\delta(t-t')Q(t)
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left[\dfrac{\partial\boldsymbol{f}}{\partial\boldsymbol{x}}\right]_{ij}\equiv\dfrac{\partial f_{i}}{\partial x_{j}}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\delta(t-t')$
\end_inset

是狄拉克
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

函数。如果过程
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\eta}_{1}(t)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\eta}_{2}(t)$
\end_inset

在统计上独立，则矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $Q(t)$
\end_inset

为块对角线矩阵，如通常假设的那样。这种协方差传播与参考文献[7-9]中的传播相同，除了一些因子是
\begin_inset Formula $\dfrac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
向量测量模型和更新
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
向量测量被建模为航天器机体坐标系中向量
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{v}_{B}$
\end_inset

的
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

个分量函数
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{h}(\boldsymbol{v}_{B})$
\end_inset

，受到零均值白噪声的破坏。机体坐标系中
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{v}_{B}$
\end_inset

的表示是通过姿态矩阵在惯性参考坐标系中表示
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{v}_{I}$
\end_inset

的映射：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{v}_{B}=A(q)\boldsymbol{v}_{I}\approx\left\{ \boldsymbol{I}_{3\times3}-[\boldsymbol{a}\times]-\dfrac{1}{2}(a^{2}\boldsymbol{I}_{3\times3}-\boldsymbol{a}\boldsymbol{a}^{T})\right\} A(q_{\mathrm{ref}})\boldsymbol{v}_{I}\label{eq:42}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中我们使用了方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:7"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)，(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:13"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)和方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:20"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)。将其替换为
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{h}(\boldsymbol{v}_{B})$
\end_inset

，并扩展到
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}$
\end_inset

中有关预更新参考的一阶项，给出
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{h}(\boldsymbol{v}_{B})=\boldsymbol{h}(\boldsymbol{\bar{v}}_{B})-\left.\dfrac{\partial\boldsymbol{h}}{\partial\boldsymbol{v}}\right|_{\boldsymbol{\bar{v}}_{B}}[\boldsymbol{a}\times]\boldsymbol{\bar{v}}_{B}=\boldsymbol{h}(\bar{\boldsymbol{v}}_{B})+H_{a}\boldsymbol{a}\label{eq:43}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\bar{v}}_{B}\equiv A(q_{\mathrm{ref}}(-))\boldsymbol{v}_{I}$
\end_inset

是由预更新四元数预测的机体坐标系向量，并且
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
H_{a}\equiv\left.\dfrac{\partial\boldsymbol{h}}{\partial\boldsymbol{v}}\right|_{\boldsymbol{\bar{v}}_{B}}[\bar{\boldsymbol{v}}_{B}\times]
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
因为测量值不明确地依赖于陀螺漂移，
\begin_inset Formula $m\times6$
\end_inset

测量灵敏度矩阵为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
H=\left[\begin{array}{cc}
\dfrac{\partial\boldsymbol{h}}{\partial\boldsymbol{a}} & \dfrac{\partial\boldsymbol{h}}{\partial\boldsymbol{b}}\end{array}\right]=\left[\begin{array}{cc}
H_{a} & 0_{m\times3}\end{array}\right]
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
卡尔曼增益矩阵由下式给出
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
K=\left[\begin{array}{c}
P_{a}(-)\\
P_{c}^{T}(-)
\end{array}\right]H_{a}^{T}\left[H_{a}P_{a}(-)H_{a}^{T}+R\right]^{-1}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

是测量白噪声的协方差。状态更新为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{\boldsymbol{x}}(+)=\hat{\boldsymbol{x}}(-)+K\left[\boldsymbol{h}_{\mathrm{obs}}-\boldsymbol{h}(\boldsymbol{\overline{v}}_{B})-H_{a}\hat{\boldsymbol{a}}(-)\right]\label{eq:47}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{h}_{\mathrm{obs}}$
\end_inset

表示测量值，并且预测值由方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:43"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)的预更新期望值给出。协方差更新是
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
P(+)=P(-)-KH_{a}\left[\begin{array}{cc}
P_{a}(-) & P_{c}(-)\end{array}\right]
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
重置
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果在每次测量更新后执行重置，方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:47"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)中的项
\begin_inset Formula $H_{a}\hat{\boldsymbol{a}}(-)$
\end_inset

等于零。为了计算效率，重置通常会延迟，直到对一组同时测量进行了所有更新，在这种情况下，方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:47"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)中的
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\boldsymbol{a}}(-)$
\end_inset

是上一次更新的
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\boldsymbol{a}}(+)$
\end_inset

。但是，在开始下一次传播之前必须执行重置，以确保传播开始时
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\boldsymbol{a}}$
\end_inset

为零，从而避免在测量之间传播
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\boldsymbol{a}}(t)$
\end_inset

。重置不会修改协方差，因为它既不会增加也不会减少估计的总信息内容；它只是将这些信息从姿态表示的一部分移动到另一部分。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
四元数测量
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
许多现代的恒星跟踪器同时跟踪
\begin_inset Formula $5$
\end_inset

到
\begin_inset Formula $50$
\end_inset

颗恒星，将它们与内部恒星目录中的恒星匹配，并将它们的姿态计算为一个惯性参考四元数[32,34]。计算还产生姿态误差角
\begin_inset Formula $3\times3$
\end_inset

协方差的估计[35,36]。将这些量从恒星跟踪器参考坐标系转换到航天器坐标系是一件简单的事情，以产生四元数“测量”值
\begin_inset Formula $q_{\mathrm{obs}}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $3\times3$
\end_inset

测量协方差矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

。将这些信息呈现给卡尔曼滤波器最方便的方法是根据观测和预测姿态之间的偏差采用一种三维参数化方法[37]
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
q_{\mathrm{obs}}=\delta q(\boldsymbol{a}_{\mathrm{obs}})\otimes q_{\mathrm{ref}}(-)\label{eq:49}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
测量模型很简单
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{h}(\boldsymbol{a})=\boldsymbol{a}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
所以
\begin_inset Formula $H_{a}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $3\times3$
\end_inset

单位矩阵，
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

是这个误差角的协方差。由于观测的预测值与方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:49"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)相同为零，因此状态更新简化为：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{\boldsymbol{x}}(+)=\hat{\boldsymbol{x}}(-)+\left[\begin{array}{c}
P_{a}(-)\\
P_{c}^{T}(-)
\end{array}\right]\left[P_{a}(-)+R\right]^{-1}\left[\boldsymbol{a}_{\mathrm{obs}}-\hat{\boldsymbol{a}}(-)\right]
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在观测处理中使用与重置中相同的三维参数化非常重要[方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:49"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)]。例如，如果方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:34"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)选择吉布斯向量[22]形式用于观测处理，则选择方程式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:18b"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)应用于重置。有了这个条件，我们可以看到，当
\begin_inset Formula $R\ll P_{a}(-)$
\end_inset

，使得
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\boldsymbol{a}}(+)=\boldsymbol{a}_{\mathrm{obs}}$
\end_inset

时，我们有
\begin_inset Formula $q_{\mathrm{ref}}=q_{\mathrm{obs}}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
二阶滤波器
\end_layout

